name: The Pact
overview: Piotr Grodecki is an investigative journalist uncovering corruption and scandals at the highest levels of government.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: In season one, with the help of Weroniki, a Central Bureau of Investigation agent, Piotr investigates a large financial scandal with far reaching consequences.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: In season two, Piotr uncovers a sex scandal involving one of the ministers. With determination, he fights to balance two difficult tasks - revealing the details of the case and protecting the young victims of sexual abuse.
